	<span class="cff-text" data-color="">Stable View is looking forward to welcoming Riders to the first stand-alone Intercollegiate, Interscholastic, and Alumni Championships.<br /><br />Last year there were 40 Team entries.<br /><br />Stable View has challenged itself to increase the number of teams by 25%.<br /><br />This will mean potentially welcoming 10 additional teams.<br /><br />Stable View’s job is to raise the profile of this event and achieve this objective - with your help - via an aggressive social media campaign.<br /><br />For those eligible riders who can return, welcome back!<br /><br />For those who are hearing about the Championships for the first time, please sign up for the Stable View Intercollegiate/Interscholastic WhatsApp group using the link in bio🔗<br /><br />For those who have graduated, please don’t forget - you can now represent your old College in a new team.<br /><br />Please reshare this post with all interested parties. 	</span>
	<span class="cff-expand">... <a href="#" ><span class="cff-more">See More</span><span class="cff-less">See Less</span></a></span>
</p>
<div class="cff-date  cff-date-below" >
	 5 days ago </div></div><div class="cff-media-wrap"><div class="cff-photo nofancybox"  data-cff-page-name="Stable View" data-cff-post-time="5 days ago" data-img-src-set="[{&quot;130&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/scontent-lax3-1.xx.fbcdn.net\/v\/t51.82787-15\/638869273_18541084879066144_133436393065617517_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_s130x130_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=110&amp;ccb=1-7&amp;_nc_sid=13d280&amp;_nc_ohc=XlU-AwXLxCcQ7kNvwFhlRYg&amp;_nc_oc=AdmvC2BUgZM-uRQT1wgDgmb3VIL8F9plLiRQ8X1OhV1hMHlg2J1VhrgtoTCES2n5SXc&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-lax3-1.xx&amp;edm=AKIiGfEEAAAA&amp;_nc_gid=P8jIi8Fu4r3OlNCruqFVkA&amp;_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQFg7Xoe6iD3RATL3K6x7hgrKhfFp667ZTjiHjEXwuszMQhP-4dwgBR7Qozif9KTNRBejTrrL8AnMg&amp;oh=00_AftOWxMw-nAjMkqmTjrlVSAquJwVn4TvCqsRvmvcrCPPEw&amp;oe=69A269D0&quot;,&quot;720&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/scontent-lax3-1.xx.fbcdn.net\/v\/t51.82787-15\/638869273_18541084879066144_133436393065617517_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_p720x720_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=110&amp;ccb=1-7&amp;_nc_sid=13d280&amp;_nc_ohc=XlU-AwXLxCcQ7kNvwFhlRYg&amp;_nc_oc=AdmvC2BUgZM-uRQT1wgDgmb3VIL8F9plLiRQ8X1OhV1hMHlg2J1VhrgtoTCES2n5SXc&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-lax3-1.xx&amp;edm=AKIiGfEEAAAA&amp;_nc_gid=P8jIi8Fu4r3OlNCruqFVkA&amp;_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQErSgukfmBXbq1X89VmCW9Bv110yvNNJdNWRfoRBexWoo3y_eyxjpF9tzzeQmfRxDM0qy1UkaRuwA&amp;oh=00_AfsYwxwKSh5WbLqKbMQX_EGzRImrR454ifKgJePH6ID_8A&amp;oe=69A269D0&quot;}]" href="https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=1471499758312605&amp;set=a.508305811298676&amp;type=3" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener"><img src="https://scontent-lax3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t51.82787-15/638869273_18541084879066144_133436393065617517_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_p720x720_tt6&_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=13d280&_nc_ohc=XlU-AwXLxCcQ7kNvwFhlRYg&_nc_oc=AdmvC2BUgZM-uRQT1wgDgmb3VIL8F9plLiRQ8X1OhV1hMHlg2J1VhrgtoTCES2n5SXc&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-lax3-1.xx&edm=AKIiGfEEAAAA&_nc_gid=P8jIi8Fu4r3OlNCruqFVkA&_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQErSgukfmBXbq1X89VmCW9Bv110yvNNJdNWRfoRBexWoo3y_eyxjpF9tzzeQmfRxDM0qy1UkaRuwA&oh=00_AfsYwxwKSh5WbLqKbMQX_EGzRImrR454ifKgJePH6ID_8A&oe=69A269D0" data-orig-source="https://scontent-lax3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t51.82787-15/638869273_18541084879066144_133436393065617517_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_p720x720_tt6&_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=13d280&_nc_ohc=XlU-AwXLxCcQ7kNvwFhlRYg&_nc_oc=AdmvC2BUgZM-uRQT1wgDgmb3VIL8F9plLiRQ8X1OhV1hMHlg2J1VhrgtoTCES2n5SXc&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-lax3-1.xx&edm=AKIiGfEEAAAA&_nc_gid=P8jIi8Fu4r3OlNCruqFVkA&_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQErSgukfmBXbq1X89VmCW9Bv110yvNNJdNWRfoRBexWoo3y_eyxjpF9tzzeQmfRxDM0qy1UkaRuwA&oh=00_AfsYwxwKSh5WbLqKbMQX_EGzRImrR454ifKgJePH6ID_8A&oe=69A269D0" alt="Stable View is looking forward to welcoming Riders to the first stand-alone Intercollegiate, Interscholastic, and Alumni Championships.

Last year there were 40 Team entries.

Stable View has challenged itself to increase the number of teams by 25%.

This will mean potentially welcoming 10 additional teams.

Stable View’s job is to raise the profile of this event and achieve this objective - with your help - via an aggressive social media campaign.

For those eligible riders who can return, welcome back!

For those who are hearing about the Championships for the first time, please sign up for the Stable View Intercollegiate/Interscholastic WhatsApp group using the link in bio🔗

For those who have graduated, please don’t forget - you can now represent your old College in a new team.

Please reshare this post with all interested parties." data-querystring="stp=dst-jpg_p720x720_tt6&_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=13d280&_nc_ohc=XlU-AwXLxCcQ7kNvwFhlRYg&_nc_oc=AdmvC2BUgZM-uRQT1wgDgmb3VIL8F9plLiRQ8X1OhV1hMHlg2J1VhrgtoTCES2n5SXc&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-lax3-1.xx&edm=AKIiGfEEAAAA&_nc_gid=P8jIi8Fu4r3OlNCruqFVkA&_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQErSgukfmBXbq1X89VmCW9Bv110yvNNJdNWRfoRBexWoo3y_eyxjpF9tzzeQmfRxDM0qy1UkaRuwA&oh=00_AfsYwxwKSh5WbLqKbMQX_EGzRImrR454ifKgJePH6ID_8A&oe=69A269D0" data-ratio="1200" class="cff-multi-image cff-feed-image" /></div></div>
