<div class="cff-comments-box cff-light" data-cff-like-text="like this" data-cff-likes-text="likes this"  data-cff-reacted-text="reacted to this" data-cff-and-text="and" data-cff-other-text="other" data-cff-others-text="others" data-cff-reply-text="Reply" data-cff-replies-text="Replies" data-num="4" data-cff-meta-link-color="#" data-cff-hide-avatars="" data-cff-expand-comments="" data-cff-post-tags="on"><p class="cff-comment-likes cff-likes" ></p><p class="cff-comments cff-comment-on-facebook" ><span>1 Comment</span><a href="https://www.facebook.com/1392274051045026_1471499771645937" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" ><span class="cff-icon"><svg width="24px" height="24px" role="img" aria-hidden="true" aria-label="Comment" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512"><path d="M448 0H64C28.7 0 0 28.7 0 64v288c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64h96v84c0 7.1 5.8 12 12 12 2.4 0 4.9-.7 7.1-2.4L304 416h144c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64V64c0-35.3-28.7-64-64-64zm32 352c0 17.6-14.4 32-32 32H293.3l-8.5 6.4L192 460v-76H64c-17.6 0-32-14.4-32-32V64c0-17.6 14.4-32 32-32h384c17.6 0 32 14.4 32 32v288z"></path></svg><svg width="24px" height="24px" class="cff-svg-bg" role="img" aria-hidden="true" aria-label="background" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512"><path d="M448 0H64C28.7 0 0 28.7 0 64v288c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64h96v84c0 9.8 11.2 15.5 19.1 9.7L304 416h144c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64V64c0-35.3-28.7-64-64-64z"></path></svg></span>Comment on Facebook</a></p><div class="cff-comments-wrap" ><div class="cff-comment" id="cff_1471499771645937_1463955532113234" data-cff-comment-date=" 5 days ago "><p >And all teams- please be collecting your items for me to decorate your personal team/ college x/c jump!  Please, no paper or cardboard items as they get ruined in bad weather or the irrigation if the weather is good!  Get them to Stable View by May 1st.   Label your boxes clearly with the name of your team, please.  Also, let Stable View know your team colors so that we can use appropriate flowers.  Thanks!  Looking forward to a great show!</p></div></div></div></div><div class="cff-item cff-photo-post author-stable-view cff-1392274051045026 cff-new" id="cff_1392274051045026_1467883212007593" data-page-id="1392274051045026" data-cff-timestamp="1771095196" data-object-id="1467883188674262" data-cff-from="1392274051045026" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #; z-index: 10;"><div class="cff-text-wrapper"><p  class="cff-post-text">
	<span class="cff-text" data-color="">It’s CLOSING DAY for the February Eventing Academy, February 20 - 22 @stableviewaiken.<br /><br />Link in bio to register!<br /> <br /><a href="https://facebook.com/167809483369785"  rel="nofollow noopener">#Equestrian</a> <a href="https://facebook.com/143697675799578"  rel="nofollow noopener">#Horseshows</a> <a href="https://facebook.com/155075387984524"  rel="nofollow noopener">#Horseshowlife</a> <a href="https://facebook.com/116670415186480"  rel="nofollow noopener">#Horseriding</a> <a href="https://facebook.com/461165393956605"  rel="nofollow noopener">#Horselife</a> 	</span>
	<span class="cff-expand">... <a href="#" ><span class="cff-more">See More</span><span class="cff-less">See Less</span></a></span>
